Introduction

YUBiKiRi is a South Korean J-POP live idol duo, consisting of Yeoul and Danko.

The group debuted as a trio with members Yeoul, Ruri, and Kine on January 29, 2023 at ‘YUB!KiRi DEBUT LIVE’ and released their official debut song ‘Eieio! (에이에이오!)’ on July 17th the same year.
